###################### Autowired ################################

Autowired byType : for a bean their should be only one property of one type and also only one bean should be in xml of that type

Autowired By Constructor : for this constructor should have arguments of different type.

######################### Bean Scopes #################################

Singleton : Only per Spring Container.
Prototype : New bean created with every request or reference.

Web-aware Context Bean Scopes

Request : New bean per Servlet request.
Session : New bean per session.
Global sesssion : New bean per global HHTP session (portlet context)
